text: The Social Democratic Party is a big political party in Romania. It started in January of 2001.It has been in a political association called "Uniunea Socială Liberală" along with the National Liberal Party that in 2014 has ended. Now it is in association with PC and UNPR (commonly known as USD). ==References== == Other websites == * Official website Category:Socialist International Category:Social democratic parties in Europe Category:Political parties in Romania Category:2001 establishments in Europe Category:2000s establishments in Romania
